//|                 and Jacobian jac at given point x                |
//|     rep     -   optional callback which is called after each     |
//|                 iteration can be null                            |
//|     obj     -   optional object which is passed to               |
//|                 func/grad/hess/jac/rep can be null               |
//| NOTES:                                                           |
