//| Complemented incomplete gamma integral                           |
//| The function is defined by                                       |
//|  igamc(a,x)   =   1 - igam(a,x)                                  |
//|                            inf.                                  |
//|                              -                                   |
//|                     1       | |  -t  a-1                         |
//|               =   -----     |   e   t   dt.                      |
//|                    -      | |                                    |
//|                   | (a)    -                                     |
//|                             x                                    |
