//| Incomplete beta integral                                         |
//| Returns incomplete beta integral of the arguments, evaluated     |
//| from zero to x.  The function is defined as                      |
//|                  x                                               |
//|     -            -                                               |
//|    | (a+b)      | |  a-1     b-1                                 |
//|  -----------    |   t   (1-t)   dt.                              |
//|   -     -     | |                                                |
//|  | (a) | (b)   -                                                 |
//|                 0                                                |
