//| formula.                                                         |
//| This routine calculates                                          |
//|     c[0]*T0(x) + c[1]*T1(x) + ... + c[N]*TN(x)                   |
//| or                                                               |
//|     c[0]*U0(x) + c[1]*U1(x) + ... + c[N]*UN(x)                   |
//| depending on the R.                                              |
//| Parameters:                                                      |
//|     r   -   polynomial kind, either 1 or 2.                      |
//|     n   -   degree, n>=0                                         |
